<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.2.9">
<l>peruku kāta laṭiyē ṉuḷḷam</l>
<l>urukap pukunta voruva rūrpōl</l>
<l>aruku kaitai malara keṇṭai</l>
<l>kurukeṉ ṟañcuṅ kūṭa lūrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Kūṭalūr, where keṇṭai [fish] fear that there is a heron</l>
<l>When the nearby screw pines blossom,</l>
<l>It seems, is the city of the one who entered the heart</l>
<l>Of this devotee, me, whose love overflows, so that it melts.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
